title: HOUR 1 - Dallas Cowboys, Steve Nash
itunes:title: HOUR 1 - Dallas Cowboys, Steve Nash
description:
In hour 1, Colin addresses the main issue holding America's team back. Which is Dak Prescott's massive and undeserving contract. Steve Nash and the Brooklyn Nets parted ways, but Colin believes its because he became a babysitter over a head coach. And building a team around Kyrie Irving is not conducive to success
